---
title: Chickpea Shakshuka with Sesame Flatbreads and Feta
description: This dish – a breakfast staple in North Africa and parts of the Middle East – relies on tomatoes, peppers, eggs and a whole slew of spices. We've added chickpeas to this version for extra nutrition. Make sure you mop up every morsel with the nutty sesame flatbread!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chakchouka-aux-pois-chiches-e16ce71e.jpg
